### ===================================================
### SEARCH PUBLISHED CHALLENGES ENDPOINT
### ===================================================

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8083/api/v1
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Search by name - find challenges containing "hello"
GET {{baseUrl}}/challenges/search?name=hello
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Search by partial name - find challenges containing "h"
GET {{baseUrl}}/challenges/search?name=h
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Search by difficulty - EASY challenges only
GET {{baseUrl}}/challenges/search?difficulty=EASY
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Search by difficulty - MEDIUM challenges only
GET {{baseUrl}}/challenges/search?difficulty=MEDIUM
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Search by difficulty - HARD challenges only
GET {{baseUrl}}/challenges/search?difficulty=HARD
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Search combining name and difficulty
GET {{baseUrl}}/challenges/search?name=sort&difficulty=MEDIUM
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Search by tags - find challenges with "arrays" or "loops"
GET {{baseUrl}}/challenges/search?tags=arrays,loops
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Search by single tag
GET {{baseUrl}}/challenges/search?tags=algorithms
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Search combining name, difficulty and tags
GET {{baseUrl}}/challenges/search?name=find&difficulty=HARD&tags=algorithms,binary-search
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Search with no filters (returns all published challenges)
GET {{baseUrl}}/challenges/search
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Search case-insensitive name
GET {{baseUrl}}/challenges/search?name=HELLO
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Search with URL-encoded spaces
GET {{baseUrl}}/challenges/search?name=hello%20world
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

